    "body": "To give an update, this indeed seems to be a compiler bug. When encoding the value from storage, the ABI routine is using `64` bytes (length (0) + 32-byte value (0)). Whereas for memory it is using 32 bytes: length (0). Made https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/12880 to track this.",
